browsertime: Chrome 73 vs GVE 68 ARM vs Fenix 68 ARM vs Fennec 64 on the Moto G5

Nick Alexander

April 08, 2019

Per-device, per-site vehicle comparisons

The following graph gives insight into how the vehicles compare on the sites in the test corpus. Generally we see Chrome 73 fastest, followed by GVE 68 ARM, followed closely by Fenix 68 AMR. Fenix 64 is significantly slower than all other vehicles. The gap between GVE and Fenix is almost “pure overhead”: things that Fenix does to support tracking protection, providing UI updates, scheduling tasks, etc.
